#: 3c6e243e0102404d9eff5c3b96519459 of unit.servo360.Servo360Unit:1
msgid "Control a 360-degree continuous rotation servo motor."
msgstr "控制 360 度连续旋转舵机。"

#: 2caacdab839c4dab82ab1aae5858a63f of unit.servo360.Servo360Unit:5
msgid ""
"For Servo Kit 360°, the duty cycle microseconds count controls rotation "
"speed and direction: **count_low** corresponds to maximum clockwise "
"speed, **count_high** to maximum counterclockwise speed, and the "
"**midpoint** value indicates stop. Values in **count_low** ~ **midpoint**"
" rotate clockwise (smaller values = faster speed), while values in "
"**midpoint** ~ **count_high** rotate counterclockwise (larger values = "
"faster speed). **midpoint** controls the stop position."
msgstr ""
"对于 Servo Kit 360°，占空比微秒计数用于控制旋转速度与方向：**count_low** "
"对应顺时针最大速度，**count_high** 对应逆时针最大速度，**midpoint** 值表示停止。取值在 **count_low** ~"
" **midpoint** 范围内时顺时针旋转（值越小速度越快），取值在 **midpoint** ~ **count_high** "
"范围内时逆时针旋转（值越大速度越快）。**midpoint** 用于控制停止位置。"

